<para style="p"> <verse number="1" style="v" />This is the beginning of the gospel of Jesus Christ, the Son of God. </para> <para style="p"> <verse number="2" style="v" />As it is written in Isaiah the prophet,  </para> <para style="q1">"Look, I am sending my messenger before you, </para> <para style="q1">the one who will prepare your way.</para> <para style="q1"> <verse number="3" style="v" />The voice of someone calling out in the wilderness, </para> <para style="q1">'Make ready the way of the Lord;</para> <para style="q1">make his paths straight.'"
